title: Fourth Floor (Part 1)
body:
Fourth Floor (Part 1)

"Who the hell is this guy?"

"He already replaced the names of the first three floors."

"Forget about replacing the names, it is not even one hour since he entered the dungeon but he already cleared three floors. Does it even make sense?"

The atmosphere outside of the dungeon was quite chaotic as people talked to each other with a look of disbelief on their faces.

All of them had their eyes fixed on the holographic screen and they were looking at it with a shocked look on their faces.

Forget about the people, even Mogul was completely stunned, especially after seeing the time that Evan took to clear the third floor.

"Just what the hell is going on inside?" Mogul muttered with a dazed look as he looked at the holographic screen using his spiritual senses.

// Second Floor. Evan. 38M. 21Sec.//

// Third Floor. Evan. 3M. 19Sec.//
